                                                                                    strESSFormat,
                                                                                    GlobalSettings.CultureInfo), token)
                                                         .ConfigureAwait(false);
                            }
                            else
                                await lblCyberwareEssence.DoThreadSafeAsync(
                                                             x => x.Text = 0.0m.ToString(strESSFormat,
                                                                 GlobalSettings.CultureInfo), token)
