                                                            .CultureInfo), token)
                                                    .ConfigureAwait(false);
                            await lblCyberwareCapacity
                                  .DoThreadSafeAsync(x => x.Text = objCyberware.DisplayCapacity, token)
                                  .ConfigureAwait(false);
